fields.name: Apartment 1
fields.description:
Located at the heart of Zadar, our apartment offers a blend of comfort and convenience. The apartment features two spacious bedrooms, ensuring ample resting space for our guests. Its functional kitchen flows seamlessly into the dining area, catering to all culinary needs during your stay. Additionally, the bathroom is equipped with a standard shower, providing a refreshing experience. For those longer stays, a washing machine is also at your disposal to take care of your laundry needs. 

The living room not only serves as a relaxation hub with a TV for entertainment but also has the added advantage of a convertible couch. This couch can be transformed into a comfortable bed suitable for two kids. To top it all, there's an attached balcony, allowing guests to enjoy some quiet outdoor moments.
